{
  "texts": [
    "In our experiments, 30-40 frames are recommended in most cases which are able to capture sufficient RGB and motion details as ascertained by the empirical results.",
    "Image resolutions of 115-126 are also mostly selected to balance between performance and computational cost.",
    "Automated hyperparameter search for EfficientNet-GRUWe also employ the same experimental settings for hyperparameter search using the EfficientNet-GRU model.",
    "A set of 5 runs is performed for hyperparameter search for each search algorithm.",
    "The optimized settings obtained by each search method are used to establish the final models, which are trained using the training set of the combined dataset with a larger number of epochs."
  ]
}